<p><a name="References_2" id="References_2"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Case_citation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h3>
<ul>
